    <title>浅析Python元类及应用</title>
    <link href="https://anniywell.github.io/2017/06/16/%E6%B5%85%E6%9E%90Python%E5%85%83%E7%B1%BB%E5%8F%8A%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8/"/>
